me.choco.locksecurity.registration

Class PlayerRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.choco.locksecurity.registration.PlayerRegistry

  • public class PlayerRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    A registry to keep track of players and their information. Any player that has every joined the server should be registered in this registry upon joining.
    Author:
    Parker Hawke - 2008Choco
